quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  19,65,"Rabbu assamawati wal-ardiwama baynahuma faAAbudhu wastabirliAAibadatihi hal taAAlamu lahu samiyya"
  19,66,"Wayaqoolu al-insanu a-itha mamittu lasawfa okhraju hayya"
  19,67,"Awa la yathkuru al-insanuanna khalaqnahu min qablu walam yaku shay-a"
  19,68,"Fawarabbika lanahshurannahum washshayateenathumma lanuhdirannahum hawla jahannama jithiyya"
  19,69,"Thumma lananziAAanna min kulli sheeAAatinayyuhum ashaddu AAala arrahmaniAAitiyya"
  19,70,"Thumma lanahnu aAAlamu billatheenahum awla biha siliyya"
  19,71,"Wa-in minkum illa wariduhakana AAala rabbika hatman maqdiyya"
  19,72,"Thumma nunajjee allatheena ittaqawwanatharu aththalimeena feehajithiyya"
  19,73,"Wa-itha tutla AAalayhim ayatunabayyinatin qala allatheena kafaroo lillatheenaamanoo ayyu alfareeqayni khayrun maqaman waahsanunadiyya"
  19,74,"Wakam ahlakna qablahum min qarnin humahsanu athathan wari/ya"
  19,75,"Qul man kana fee addalalatifalyamdud lahu arrahmanu maddan hattaitha raaw ma yooAAadoona imma alAAathabawa-imma assaAAata fasayaAAlamoona man huwasharrun makanan waadAAafu junda"
  19,76,"Wayazeedu Allahu allatheenaihtadaw hudan walbaqiyatu assalihatukhayrun AAinda rabbika thawaban wakhayrun maradda"
